-### Reward Calculation
-- **Base coins**: `score // 10` (minimum 1)
-- **Base XP**: `score // 5` (minimum 5)
-- **High score bonus**: +25 coins, +50 XP
-- **Streak bonus**: `min(streak * 10, 100)` coins
